{"word":"παλαμάομαι","slug":"παλαμάομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>παλαμάομαι</b></el> <el>(πᾰλᾰμάομαι,) </el><p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to manage, execute</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>like <el>μηχανάομαι</el>, <i>to manage adroitly, contrive cunningly</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <el>πaλάμη</el>\n"}]}